original_title: Pro Wrestling's Ultimate Insiders Vol. 2: Inside WCW
overview: Inside WCW focuses on the duo's highly controversial jump from the WWF to Ted Turner's WCW and the professional and personal chaos that would follow. Hear inside stories on Goldberg, Sting, Kevin Nash, DDP, Eric Bishoff, Hulk Hogan, and more.
title: Pro Wrestling's Ultimate Insiders Vol. 2: Inside WCW
